### Command Reference Table

|Command|What it does|When to use|
|---|---|---|
|`idf.py create-project NAME`|Creates new project folder|Once at start|
|`idf.py set-target esp32`|Sets target chip|Once per project|
|`idf.py menuconfig`|Opens config UI|When changing settings|
|`idf.py build`|Compiles project|After every code change|
|`idf.py flash`|Flashes to board|After build|
|`idf.py monitor`|Opens serial monitor|To see output|
|`idf.py flash monitor`|Flash then monitor|Most common combo|
|`idf.py fullclean`|Deletes build folder|When build is broken|
|`idf.py size`|Shows binary size|When debugging memory|
|`idf.py -p COM3 flash`|Flash to specific port|Windows|
|`idf.py -p /dev/ttyUSB0 flash`|Flash to specific port|Linux/Mac|

